@Comment:	Time is 0:04
@Comment:	Chi reads at the table with Mot watching from a few feet away; Chi is a pretty competent reader I'd say -- I think he uses both print and context to help him get through; after apple Mot says he's not reading the words and says to follow word with finger; Mot's comments include sound it out put your finger under it , encouraging remarks , and occasionally giving the word; context notes mention subtle encouragement like smiling and nodding; one thing that strikes me is Chi's questioning tone when he knows he's guessing , and guessing wrong
